    {
        "content": "<p>i think the main issue here is that single-line <code>calc</code> tactics have trouble being parsed as intended, and are typically unnecessary. with regards to <code>\\.</code>: put the <code>left</code> and <code>right</code> <em>after</em> the <code>\\.</code>, not before.</p>",
